description: Welcome to The Dino Smile.The Dino Smile are a collection of 1,111 randomly generated NFTs on the Ethereum blockchain.We rise together. We build together. We grow together.Join us to be a part of our journey building something special -20% of the proceeds will go to donations to help children in the greatest need, targeting African countries. Where children are at greatest risk and deprivation - the significance, gratitude and joy of helping hand are the most sincere.We make the world better,with a smile
